#### make array of string characters;
string.split(separator, limit)

separator	(Optional):Specifies the character,
                      or the regular expression, to use for splitting the string. 
                      If omitted, the entire string will be returned (an array with only one item)

limit	(Optiona)l :An integer that specifies the number of splits, 
                  items after the split limit will not be included in the array.
var res = str.split("");
if specify "" in split it will return all characters in array.
